<bibRefCitation id="733DDCEF6B49D315DA10746AFD017FA2" author="Hackman" box="[544,721,1663,1688]" pageId="16" pageNumber="67" refString="Hackman, W. (1976) De som larver i hattsvampar levande anthomyiidernas biologi (Diptera) [The biology of anthomyiid flies feeding as larvae in fungi (Diptera).] Notulae entomologicae, 56, 129 - 134. [In Swedish with English summary.]" type="journal article" year="1976">
