) reared from larvae in bolete sporocarps of the 
<taxonomicName id="D0ACDA9D6B49D315DA2574B0FD397F86" box="[533,745,1699,1724]" class="Agaricomycetes" family="Boletaceae" genus="Leccinum" kingdom="Fungi" order="Boletales" pageId="16" pageNumber="67" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="species" species="scabrum">
